Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:10.00,AKT-TEAM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(104,29)\fad(500,500)}AKT-TEAM Vám prináša
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:12.00,AKT-TEAM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(203,57)\fad(500,500)}www.anikiteam.org
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:14.00,x3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(505,44)}Preložil
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:16.00,Saphirro,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(555,75)}Saphirro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:19.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach nie! Spravila som to!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedz, si v poriadku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:26.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neobyčajne.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:28.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Si zranený?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:34.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Som v poriadku, v poriadku. Povedz, nie je to BMW Isetta 300?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:35.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:36.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto... vidíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:40.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to starší model, ktorý robil iný výrobca.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:45.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môj je originálna Isetta, vyrobená spoločnosťou Iso. Je to Isetta 250.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:48.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Originál, čo? Je tvoje?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:54.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jo. Nechal mi ho dedo. Už má skoro 70 rokov.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.26,0:00:57.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty tiež? Tiež mám jedno.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:00.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach? Tiež chceš do Aquariona?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:13.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}V 1. dni na svete, pod stromom života,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.68,0:01:20.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}dvaja z nás počuli hlasy veľrýb, odrážajúce sa z diaľky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:26.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}So všetkým, čo sme stratili a všetko, čo sme milovali,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:33.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}čo sme mali v náručí, kam sa to zatúľalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:39.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Odpoveď leží v jantári slnka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:45.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Ak by som ťa nestretla, zničila by som anjela.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:51.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Moja duša posadnutá okamihom nesmrteľnosti,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:54.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}nezraní moje krídla.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:02:01.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Zrodila som sa, aby som spoznala tento pocit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:08.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po 1.000 rokov a ešte ďalších 2.000, som ťa ľúbila.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:14.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po 8.000 rokoch, som ťa ľúbila ešte viac.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:20.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po ďalších 100.000.000 rokov a ešte ďalších 2.000, ťa budem stále ľúbiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:29.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Od 1. dňa, keď som ťa spoznala, hudba v mojom pekle nikdy neprestala.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:43.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1500)\pos(310,214)}Škola elementov
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:51.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Som z územia 17 v Neo-Ázii.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:57.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Volám sa Jun Lee. Teší ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:03.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Som Tsugumi Rosenmeier zo severnej obrannej zóny Belman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:09.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Som Pierre! Tsugumi, aké sú tvoje zámery?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Musím to povedať?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vy dvaja si sadnite vedľa Pierra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:26.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Pale Mucho Perishable"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:24.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa, Sophia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zaberie to nejaký čas, kým ho sem dostaneme.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:33.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A tu je ďalší. Nájdený v meste Arc...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten potkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:44.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to za miesto? Všetci vyzeráte tak smutne. Ako prasatá v ohrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:49.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty máš čo hovoriť! A ako si sa opovážil zničiť moje 1. zjednotenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:56.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, je to ten chalan, ktorý zničí vojaka Cherubína?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:58.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vravia, že je znovuzrodené Slnečné Krídlo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale je len dieťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto je Slnečné Krídlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:06.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,No to je... Je to iné meno Apolloniusa,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:08.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,legendárny hrdina, o ktorom sa píše
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:11.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,v svätej knihe starej ríše Alisia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:16.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pred 12,000 rokmi, spolu so Seliane a inými používateľmi elementov,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:20.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,riadil Aquariona a bojoval s Tieňovými anjelmi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:21.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to všetko vieš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:24.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to prísne tajné zaradenie AAA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:30.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Firewall Deavu je hračka pre mňa... bývalý princ Sirius de Alisia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:32.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:33.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hackol si sa im do sytémov?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:37.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoci, som si neuvedomil, že ma našli.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:41.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je tá obrovská mašina! Musím ísť zachrániť Barona.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Musím to spraviť rýchlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:46.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, ešte si sa nič nenaučil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedostaneš ma 2 krát rovnakým trikom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:06.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty zviera! Neuvedomuješ si, čo si spravil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:10.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zmĺkni! Prišiel som, lebo mi povedali, že to môžem riadiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:15.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj ho môžeš riadiť. Ak sa rozhodne, že si kompatibilný
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:18.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,v srdci, duši a tele, aby si bol elementom Aquariona.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:23.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kompatibilný?! Už som ho riadil 2 krát!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:26.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A počas toho si zničil mesto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...za hroznú vec.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:34.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo musím trénovať niečo také?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:38.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach, ale nie je Apollo jeden z tých, ktorých hľadáme?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:43.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinkarnácia starej lásky, Apolloniusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Lásky?! Nebuďte smiešna!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:48.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď je jeho meno podobné, je to len čistá náhoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:53.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeš prerezať všetky tieto rakety?! Túto hračku zvládnem sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:56.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tento simulátor je veľmi podobný.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:59.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Okrem toho, príbuzenstvo s tvojimi rodičmi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:03.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,je veľmi dôležité, pre zjednotenie s Aquarionom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:06.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Príbuzenstvo? Čo to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:11.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph, si taký hlúpy! A nemôžeš aspoň nosiť oblečenie elementov?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:12.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:19.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia, ak tvoj partner Apollo nedokáže zvládnuť reakciu riadenia,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:20.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,tak sa vrátiš na začiatok s ním.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:23.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:27.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika-sempai, žiadam o velenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:32.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion odpovedá sile svalov, srdca a duše
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:36.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,jeho používateľov elementov. Tak nebuď nervózna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:43.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika je taká láskavá.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:46.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius-sempai, prosím, začnite zľahka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:50.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto nie je hračka. Mysli na to ako na skutočnosť a ber to vážne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:51.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:54.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:58.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rýchlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! To je veľký mech!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:21.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukľudni sa, Tsugumi. Skutočný mechanizmus reakcií Aquariona
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:24.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,je oveľa citlivejší. Jemnejšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:25.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:27.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jemne, jemne...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:33.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Synchronizácia vedomia a svalov je menej ako mili sekunda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:36.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sústreď sa a harmonizuj!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:38.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Áno!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:40.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Núdzový výstup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:42.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Výstup?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:48.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechaj ma ovládať! Vector Sol, čo robíte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:50.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:54.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten hlupák sa zrazu pohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:59.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia, musíš prijať zodpovednosť za to, čo spravil tvoj partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:02.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď je horší ako zviera!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Viem to, ale bra-!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:09.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:17.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, ja s tým letím, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:22.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebuď hlúpy! Ovládam to ja!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:29.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?! Čo?! Prečo ty-! Ako sa opovažuješ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:34.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To musí byť zlý vtip... To dieťa nemôže byť reinkarnáciou Slnečného Krídla!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:38.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silviine tvrdenia o jej minulom živote sa tiež zdajú byť pochybné.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dajte ich o 2 úrovne nižšie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:47.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozrite na dynamcikú auru tých dvoch! Úroveň mysle je na celom mieste,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:51.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,ale červená oblasť duší je synchronizovaná.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:53.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Červená oblasť?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:57.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Červená vášeň. Červená, pre 1. čakru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vráť to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:01.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo robíš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:10.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dávaj pozor, cíť to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto znamená kontrolovať to... stroj Vector...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,na kontrolu Aquariona!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:23.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem... Nemôžem! Nemôžem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Prestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:35.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Duševná úroveň stúpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:39.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, nehovorte mi, že jej odmietnutie znamenalo pravý opak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:44.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak rýchlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:45.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:49.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem, nemôžem... Nemôžem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:08.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Šla som a spravila som to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:12.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo to... Ak to skúsi znova...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:22.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa... Nešlo mi to dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:28.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neospravedlňuj sa. Keby som ťa lepšie viedla...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ona nevedela...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:37.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by som si viedla lepšie... efektívnejšie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:44.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika? Reika-sempai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:44.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Len spomínam...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:52.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Simulátor je iný ako skutočnosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:08.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Baron...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:09.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Stále si tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:10.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:20.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo donúti toto lietať? Aké je príbuzenstvo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:22.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:26.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Neviem, preto sa pýtam! Rýchlo mi to povedz!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:27.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:31.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zase on...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:35.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Počas boja, nebol si v úplnej kontrole?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:41.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:45.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vtedy, počul som zvuk...z niekadiaľ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:47.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zvuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:55.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A myslel som si... že vidím, muža s krídlami...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Muža s krídlami?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:00.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie Slnečné Krídlo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:05.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mal obrovské krídla... a vlasy ako plamene...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:10.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A oči boli strašidelné... ale smutné.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:13.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne ako tvoje.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:18.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Strašidelné, ale trocha smutné.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Nie som smutný!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:24.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje odmietanie hovorí, že mám pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:27.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je... smutný?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:31.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A? Čo ten mu s krídlami spravil?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:32.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nespomínam si.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:35.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra! Hups!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:39.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nespomínam si, ale chcem zachrániť Barona...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:42.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a predtým, než som to vedel, som bol v tom stroji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:46.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aký je Baron?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:53.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ujal sa ma v internačnom tábore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:13:04.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol som hladný, a na pokraji smrti... a on mi dal svoje vlastné jedlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:08.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spolu sme utiekli a dal mi toto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:15.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A dal mi meno, Apollo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:18.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Apollo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:23.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu je tvoja odpoveď. Čo znamená príbuzenstvo... čo to je.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:25.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:28.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Simulácia a skutočnosť sú 2 rozdielne veci.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:31.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ľudia myslia a telá robia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:33.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:38.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje pocity k Baronovi... to je skutočnosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:41.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto začal Aquarion konať.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:44.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje pocity kontrolujú Aquariona?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:48.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oblasť zeme číslo 3! Zberač videný!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:54.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Mars, Sirius. Vector Sol, Reika. Vector Luna, Silvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:55.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pripravte sa hneď.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:58.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:13:59.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ona bola...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:01.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Uvidíme sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:05.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, počkať! Prečo nezavolali mňa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:09.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Útočíme!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:12.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika-sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:22.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:25.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kam ide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:39.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pripravte sa. Pripravte sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:41.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetky systémy bežia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:44.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Opustite palubu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:48.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Opakujem, opustite palubu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:58.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako je tomu mladíkovi? Nebol v simulačnej miestnosti?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:00.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako si to vedel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:05.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje kroky mi to povedali.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:06.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kroky?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:17.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ Fudo... mal rovnaké oči ako ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rovnaké oči?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:22.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oči beštie... to svetlo, tma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrá práca.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:32.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Mars, vzlietam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Sol, vzlietam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:38.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Luna, vzlietam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:45.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:57.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:59.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ, zastavte vzlietavanie, ihneď!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabudni na to, nechaj ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:02.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Úplne rovnaké oči.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:19.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Luna, meškáš.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:21.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ospravedlňujem sa! Mám záťaž.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Voláš ma záťaž?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aká je jeho slabina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak veľa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:43.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:47.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Našla som slabinu u Zberača! Prosím, nechajte ma zjednotiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:49.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika, našla si slabinu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:51.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak rýchlo a dovoľte mi sa zjednotiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:56.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:01.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Elektrická sieť je dole. Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:03.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika, si v poriadku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:06.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Viac dimenzionálny kvantum klesá!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:06.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Znova som to pokazila...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:08.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ, treba výmenu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:12.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre. Čakaj na výmenu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:13.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre, k službám!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:51.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Meškáš!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:18:00.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Slabé miesto zberača je...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:07.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,v strede jeho hrude... trafíme inde a ľudia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prídeme neskoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika-sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:14.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,V strede hrude, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:19.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Mars, čakajte na zjednotenie! Máte jeden pokus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:22.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dáme ho jednou ranou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:29.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkaz! Formácia M-S-L! Kódové meno: Nádherný prízrak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:33.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra! Som pozadu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:37.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach no, stále je to moje 1. zjednotenie. Zoberiem to aj tak, princezná!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:40.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre! Prestaň kecať-!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:52.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Naša formácia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:03.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sprav to, Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:20.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sú späť!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:21.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Títo dvaja...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Úroveň viac dimenzionálneho kvantuma narastá.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:25.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hodnota zjednotenia, 98%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:28.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Úroveň 3 aury zvrušenia, zadymené, ale čistí sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:30.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa s tými dvoma deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Príbuzenstvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:37.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, ledva sú v synchronizácii.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nenshin! Nenshin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:39.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Gattai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:40.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideš Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:55.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Človeče, to je horúce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:58.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:03.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nikam neodídeš!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:05.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideme! Ohnivá šabľa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohnivá...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,šabľa! Šabľa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:30.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Traja za jedného! Dajte mi vašu silu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:22.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:26.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:34.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Také nádherné...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:39.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je úžasné... Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:43.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:58.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zobral ho preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:01.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké kruté...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:04.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo ty špina...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:09.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je na nič cítiť sa frustrovane. Toto je skutočnosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:12.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Potom, čo sme ho mali...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:15.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie počkať!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:19.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočnosť...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.71,0:24:02.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun, to je ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.38,0:24:04.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi, tieto prezentačné výstrely sú nekompletné.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.18,0:24:06.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.09,0:24:08.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,No, ukáže to iba jeden charakter, tak slovo nie je čisté.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:12.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! Nabudúce v Aquarion: "Bosý bojovník"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:15.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(438,360)\fad(280)}"Bosý bojovník"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.46,0:24:13.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, prezentácia končí!
